org.opendaylight.controller.containermanager

Class ContainerConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.configuration.ConfigurationObject
      • org.opendaylight.controller.containermanager.ContainerConfig
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ContainerConfig
extends ConfigurationObject
implements java.io.Serializable
    Container Configuration Java Object for Container Manager Represents a container configuration information for Container Manager. Objects of this class are also serialized to and deserialized from binary files through java serialization API when saving to/reading from Container Manager startup configuration file.
    See Also:
